  "markup": "\u003Cp style=\u0022mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;\u0022 class=\u0022MsoNormal\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none;\u0022\u003EFor those of you who operate company vehicles or use your personal vehicles for company business, we emphasize safe driving practices and compliance with all traffic laws. You are expected to maintain a valid driver\u0027s license, appropriate insurance, and ensure your vehicle is in safe operating condition. Any accidents or traffic violations while on company business must be reported immediately. This policy is crucial for your safety and the public, as well as for protecting company assets.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;\u0022 class=\u0022MsoNormal\u0022\u003E\u0026nbsp;\u003C/p\u003E"
